 | url = http://www.theashevilletourists.com/durham.htm
 | accessdate = 2007-04-09 }}</ref> In 2003, ''[[Sports Illustrated]]'' ranked ''Bull Durham'' as the "Greatest Sports Movie".<ref name= "sportsill">{{cite news
 | last =
 | first =
 | coauthors =
