 | url = http://cgi.cnnsi.com/features/2003/si_movies/
 | accessdate = 2008-04-24 }}</ref> In addition, the film is ranked number 55 on [[Bravo (US TV channel)|Bravo's]] "100 Funniest Movies."<ref name= "bravo">{{cite news
 | last =
