 | accessdate = 2007-09-25 }}</ref> It is also ranked #97 on the [[American Film Institute|American Film Institute's]] "[[AFI's 100 Years... 100 Laughs|100 Years...100 Laughs]]" list, and #1 on [[Rotten Tomatoes]]' Top Sports Movies<ref name= "rotten">{{cite news
